00:04:05.188 --> 00:04:05.329
Now,

00:04:06.669 --> 00:04:07.691
You might say, okay, well,

00:04:07.790 --> 00:04:08.692
isn't that glorious?

00:04:08.731 --> 00:04:10.473
You were able to go back in time,

00:04:10.532 --> 00:04:11.073
Leah was,

00:04:11.153 --> 00:04:13.335
and it's clearly a one-two punch.

00:04:13.354 --> 00:04:15.736
When you read many of the other mashal,

00:04:15.757 --> 00:04:17.137
they talk about this incidence,

00:04:17.177 --> 00:04:18.538
and it's a husband and wife,

00:04:18.598 --> 00:04:19.360
it's the two of us,

00:04:20.141 --> 00:04:21.622
