00:04:22.322 --> 00:04:24.303
He needed counseling.

00:04:24.603 --> 00:04:25.964
He needed an intervention.

00:04:26.865 --> 00:04:27.485
And you might say, well,

00:04:27.545 --> 00:04:28.166
isn't that glorious?

00:04:28.187 --> 00:04:29.627
You had this opportunity to do that.

00:04:30.168 --> 00:04:30.788
Yes and no.

00:04:31.108 --> 00:04:35.052
That was another life, long,

00:04:35.091 --> 00:04:35.673
long time ago.

00:04:38.057 --> 00:04:40.300
This is a very different life.

00:04:41.961 --> 00:04:42.240
You see,

00:04:43.101 --> 00:04:47.024
what I have determined is that since God

00:04:47.064 --> 00:04:49.826
cannot take someone back in time to

00:04:49.906 --> 00:04:52.708
interact back in time without destroying

00:04:52.867 --> 00:04:53.408
the universe,

00:04:53.428 --> 00:04:55.389
it would literally rip apart the universe

00:04:55.430 --> 00:04:56.190
if you were to do so.

00:04:56.211 --> 00:04:58.672
It would change cause and effect.

00:04:58.793 --> 00:05:00.894
It's written really into the fabric of

00:05:00.973 --> 00:05:03.055
light and how light is the governing

00:05:05.137 --> 00:05:06.278
aspect of the universe.

00:05:07.644 --> 00:05:08.785
You can't go back in time.

00:05:10.185 --> 00:05:12.067
So knowing that,

00:05:12.766 --> 00:05:14.927
the only way that Yahowah could keep his

00:05:14.987 --> 00:05:17.348
plan on track when it was on the

00:05:17.488 --> 00:05:22.651
