01:12:12.708 --> 01:12:15.229
And then after his tribute to the

01:12:15.628 --> 01:12:17.470
contribution of many women,

01:12:18.748 --> 01:12:20.850
Dowd addresses the one with the character

01:12:22.051 --> 01:12:22.851
to admonish him.

01:12:25.073 --> 01:12:25.975
So in these words,

01:12:26.015 --> 01:12:29.917
the Ashar introduced by Leah and the Amah

01:12:29.978 --> 01:12:31.559
foretold by Ruwth,

01:12:31.979 --> 01:12:35.962
the M mother brought by Yah to save

01:12:36.061 --> 01:12:38.024
our savior on this occasion,

01:12:39.704 --> 01:12:42.686
is afforded a status beyond compare.

01:12:44.108 --> 01:12:46.990
We are therefore in the presence of the

01:12:48.574 --> 01:12:53.917
Greatest woman who ever lived?

01:12:53.936 --> 01:12:58.498
Well, according to Yahowah.

01:12:58.519 --> 01:12:58.979
It reads,

01:13:01.859 --> 01:13:05.601
many women have acted and engaged,

01:13:06.801 --> 01:13:10.103
having performed ably and aptly,

01:13:11.043 --> 01:13:13.024
demonstrating the power of their

01:13:13.725 --> 01:13:16.525
convictions and their noble character

01:13:17.853 --> 01:13:22.015
in highly capable competent and worthy

01:13:22.055 --> 01:13:25.697
manners demonstrating tremendous virtue

01:13:25.737 --> 01:13:28.259
and strength of courage intervening

01:13:28.319 --> 01:13:34.481
powerfully and valuably but you yourself

01:13:36.122 --> 01:13:43.447
surpass and rise above them all Mashal

01:13:43.466 --> 01:13:44.207
word picture

01:13:49.639 --> 01:13:52.520
this the final Mashal has painted the

01:13:52.560 --> 01:13:55.203
portrait of the woman who has contributed

01:13:55.283 --> 01:13:58.444
more than any other throughout time she

01:13:58.484 --> 01:14:01.466
delivered the gaal the kinsman redeemer

01:14:02.547 --> 01:14:04.988
through the Berythcovenant family she

01:14:05.029 --> 01:14:07.970
became the ‘Amah the most productive of

01:14:08.051 --> 01:14:12.274
mothers no one has offered more ashar

01:14:13.154 --> 01:14:14.996
blessings or benefits

01:14:16.877 --> 01:14:17.657
According to God,

01:14:17.737 --> 01:14:19.398
and he knows her best of all,

01:14:19.457 --> 01:14:21.677
has been with her for many thousands of

01:14:21.717 --> 01:14:22.158
years,

01:14:22.957 --> 01:14:25.719
and affirmed this now through his son,

01:14:26.259 --> 01:14:29.739
who she returned to his father.

01:14:30.899 --> 01:14:32.279
Leah's character is sublime,

01:14:32.840 --> 01:14:34.121
and her convictions are noble.

01:14:34.921 --> 01:14:36.820
She is deemed capable and competent.

01:14:37.881 --> 01:14:40.981
She engaged when others were hesitant.

01:14:42.122 --> 01:14:45.002
She performed ably and aptly.

01:14:47.713 --> 01:14:50.295
Leah demonstrated that God was right about

01:14:50.395 --> 01:14:53.837
us all along.

01:14:53.877 --> 01:14:56.417
Given the opportunity, given the time,

01:14:57.618 --> 01:15:00.340
given the right woman who was right about

01:15:00.420 --> 01:15:03.280
him, we are capable of listening.

01:15:05.181 --> 01:15:07.543
We can learn and then respond.

01:15:10.345 --> 01:15:14.207
On behalf of her and many other women,

01:15:15.310 --> 01:15:19.932
She proved herself worthy before man and

01:15:19.972 --> 01:15:20.673
before God.

01:15:23.796 --> 01:15:26.637
This is among the most amazing statements

01:15:26.658 --> 01:15:28.618
to be found anywhere in an inspired

01:15:28.658 --> 01:15:30.060
prophetic text, and it reads,

01:15:30.539 --> 01:15:32.240
Many women have acted, engaged,

01:15:32.301 --> 01:15:34.382
and performed ably and aptly,

01:15:34.422 --> 01:15:36.423
demonstrating the power of their

01:15:36.463 --> 01:15:38.125
convictions and noble character,

01:15:38.145 --> 01:15:39.546
being capable and competent.

01:15:39.987 --> 01:15:42.948
But you, yourself, surpass and rise."

01:15:43.990 --> 01:15:48.932
ascending and exalted above them all.

01:15:49.012 --> 01:15:49.514
And to think,

01:15:50.673 --> 01:15:53.314
there was actually a group of jealous and

01:15:53.355 --> 01:15:55.195
embittered women who believed that they

01:15:55.235 --> 01:15:56.497
speak for a spirit mom.

01:15:57.256 --> 01:15:58.377
A mother god, they say,

01:15:58.438 --> 01:16:00.559
is found in the eighth Mashal proverb,

01:16:01.439 --> 01:16:03.579
when it has no reference to a Ruwach

01:16:04.240 --> 01:16:04.640
or an Em.

01:16:06.260 --> 01:16:06.640
Then,

01:16:06.840 --> 01:16:09.082
not letting facts frustrate their fantasy,

01:16:09.823 --> 01:16:13.365
they Ruwthlessly and relentlessly slandered

01:16:13.426 --> 01:16:14.466
the em, a mother,

01:16:15.006 --> 01:16:16.648
hailed as the greatest of them all,

01:16:18.128 --> 01:16:19.050
along with Yada,

01:16:19.289 --> 01:16:23.012
the Baal husband of this amazing Ashar,

01:16:23.293 --> 01:16:27.716
blessed and beneficial woman.

01:16:27.777 --> 01:16:29.037
Adding to their misfortune,

01:16:29.057 --> 01:16:32.400
they would also protest that Dowd could not

01:16:32.421 --> 01:16:33.502
have fulfilled Passover,

01:16:34.505 --> 01:16:38.689
negating the entire purpose of the final

01:16:38.729 --> 01:16:39.328
word picture.

01:16:41.770 --> 01:16:46.615
That is why Yahowah took keen aim at

01:16:46.655 --> 01:16:46.876
them,

01:16:47.555 --> 01:16:49.497
denouncing and destroying them in the

01:16:49.537 --> 01:16:52.761
fifty-seventh chapter of Yashayah, Isaiah,

01:16:53.421 --> 01:16:56.884
before dispatching them to Sheowl,

01:16:58.345 --> 01:16:58.985
but even more.

01:16:59.929 --> 01:17:03.331
They get a dishonorable mention by Dowd

01:17:03.890 --> 01:17:06.632
here at the conclusion of the Last Mashal.

01:17:07.934 --> 01:17:12.195
Turns out the king hates them as much

01:17:12.275 --> 01:17:13.516
as does his father.

01:17:16.519 --> 01:17:20.902
This reads this disingenuous and vain

01:17:20.942 --> 01:17:25.243
display of compassion and favoritism for

01:17:25.363 --> 01:17:26.164
popular appeal

01:17:28.426 --> 01:17:30.728
is meaningless and it's futile.

01:17:31.988 --> 01:17:36.230
It's an idolatrous pursuit and it's wasted

01:17:36.291 --> 01:17:36.712
breath.

01:17:39.712 --> 01:17:41.914
A woman who is brilliant and beautiful,

01:17:43.975 --> 01:17:45.537
reveres and respects Yahowah.

01:17:48.037 --> 01:17:51.159
It is she who is to be independently

01:17:51.199 --> 01:17:54.681
admired and celebrated without compulsion,

01:17:55.609 --> 01:17:58.970
for radiating her brilliant and clear

01:17:59.351 --> 01:17:59.731
light.

01:18:00.512 --> 01:18:02.073
It is she who is to be extolled.

01:18:02.673 --> 01:18:03.675
On your own initiative,

01:18:04.435 --> 01:18:06.176
for being worthy of exaltation,

01:18:06.216 --> 01:18:07.377
for beaming brightly.

01:18:09.038 --> 01:18:11.440
Mashal, word picture, Proverb thirty, one,

01:18:11.600 --> 01:18:14.382
thirty.

01:18:14.403 --> 01:18:14.983
Lay is the one.

01:18:16.163 --> 01:18:19.086
One in eight billion who would thwart the

01:18:19.926 --> 01:18:23.088
insidious pleas for popularity of a futile

01:18:23.248 --> 01:18:23.409
eight.

01:18:24.278 --> 01:18:26.319
who engendered Yahowah's wrath.

01:18:27.180 --> 01:18:29.841
Her brilliance and beauty win the day

01:18:30.721 --> 01:18:32.923
because she reveres and respects Yahowah.

01:18:34.185 --> 01:18:35.865
There is no better informed,

01:18:35.926 --> 01:18:40.168
no wiser or more beneficial approach than

01:18:40.208 --> 01:18:40.569
this.

01:18:42.550 --> 01:18:45.332
So my beloved wife, my present from God,

01:18:45.733 --> 01:18:47.974
Yahowah's gift to every man and woman in

01:18:48.014 --> 01:18:48.975
the covenant family

01:18:50.167 --> 01:18:53.791
should be admired, indeed celebrated,

01:18:54.372 --> 01:18:55.773
for all that she has accomplished.

01:18:56.153 --> 01:18:56.793
Keep in mind,

01:18:56.894 --> 01:18:59.355
this request is being offered by Dowd,

01:18:59.475 --> 01:19:01.518
the most acclaimed of men.

01:19:03.359 --> 01:19:05.681
A man that never respected a woman for

01:19:05.721 --> 01:19:07.623
being anything more than a physical body

01:19:07.684 --> 01:19:14.390
is now saying this of a woman.

01:19:14.430 --> 01:19:16.692
He said so because Leah enlightened him.

01:19:18.359 --> 01:19:20.359
He said so because he discovered that a

01:19:20.378 --> 01:19:22.439
woman's beauty was more than skin deep.

01:19:23.960 --> 01:19:27.400
He said so because she earned his respect.

01:19:28.661 --> 01:19:31.801
He said so because she had more respect

01:19:31.841 --> 01:19:33.981
for Yahowah than he had shown.

01:19:35.903 --> 01:19:39.783
He said so because she had not intervened,

01:19:39.863 --> 01:19:41.163
had she not intervened,

01:19:41.844 --> 01:19:44.965
his life and ours were essentially over.

01:19:46.974 --> 01:19:48.914
The ‘Amah, productive mother of Yahowah,

01:19:49.435 --> 01:19:50.676
would be an Ashar,

01:19:50.716 --> 01:19:52.456
beneficial blessing for all.

01:19:53.697 --> 01:19:57.417
And it is her garment of luminosity that's

01:19:57.438 --> 01:20:00.859
going to adorn every child born into the

01:20:00.880 --> 01:20:01.720
Beryth covenant,

01:20:02.420 --> 01:20:08.502
beginning with God's firstborn, Dowd.

01:20:08.523 --> 01:20:12.243
It is the fruit of the loom,

01:20:12.344 --> 01:20:13.444
as the fruit of her hands.

01:20:14.792 --> 01:20:17.494
you all have decided to entrust her as

01:20:17.534 --> 01:20:17.956
a gift.

01:20:19.056 --> 01:20:21.338
And so you should choose to be productive

01:20:21.378 --> 01:20:23.640
for her.

01:20:23.720 --> 01:20:24.622
Of your own accord,

01:20:25.122 --> 01:20:28.404
you are all appointed as a gift,

01:20:28.926 --> 01:20:31.027
present for her when approaching her and

01:20:31.488 --> 01:20:32.809
producing for her.

01:20:34.711 --> 01:20:36.752
And so her contributions and

01:20:36.853 --> 01:20:40.475
accomplishments will exclaim that she is

01:20:40.536 --> 01:20:41.195
praiseworthy,

01:20:41.235 --> 01:20:41.577
she is

01:20:43.274 --> 01:20:45.814
Worthy by acknowledging her brilliant

01:20:46.194 --> 01:20:49.136
radiance and clear light from within the

01:20:49.216 --> 01:20:52.597
inter sanctum of the thoughtful assembly.

01:20:53.358 --> 01:20:54.297
Inside the doors,

01:20:54.337 --> 01:20:57.198
the gates and the portal of the community

01:20:57.319 --> 01:20:59.119
of rational thinkers.

01:21:00.621 --> 01:21:04.301
Mashal word picture, Proverbs, thirty-one,

01:21:04.341 --> 01:21:04.881
thirty-one.

01:21:07.962 --> 01:21:09.304
In the ninth chapter of Isaiah,

01:21:10.423 --> 01:21:12.064
we learned that a son was given

01:21:13.119 --> 01:21:14.779
And the thirty first Mashal,

01:21:15.761 --> 01:21:18.520
we know who gift wrapped him and who

01:21:18.581 --> 01:21:21.902
delivered him to us.

01:21:21.921 --> 01:21:24.502
It's quite an accomplishment because it

01:21:24.563 --> 01:21:32.925
means that a woman saved the world.

01:21:32.984 --> 01:21:35.386
Now I will stop here.

01:21:36.765 --> 01:21:36.826
Uh,

01:21:36.845 --> 01:21:40.067
we're at a hour and twenty one minutes

01:21:40.127 --> 01:21:40.947
into this program.

01:21:42.636 --> 01:21:46.100
I have a recap of this entire Mashal

01:21:46.140 --> 01:21:46.979
from beginning to end.

01:21:49.181 --> 01:21:52.604
And I have a recap that is different

01:21:52.623 --> 01:21:53.725
than any other I've ever done.

01:21:54.605 --> 01:21:56.806
Rather than just starting with the first

01:21:56.907 --> 01:22:00.250
statement of the thirty-first Mashal,

01:22:00.310 --> 01:22:01.350
the final word picture,

01:22:02.411 --> 01:22:09.176
I actually share the prophecies that

01:22:09.216 --> 01:22:09.837
foretell of it.

01:22:11.335 --> 01:22:16.057
What Yahowah said in the garden about Adam

01:22:16.078 --> 01:22:17.658
and Chawah beginning again.

01:22:19.418 --> 01:22:23.020
What Leah had to offer to this

01:22:23.060 --> 01:22:23.822
conversation.

01:22:24.662 --> 01:22:26.483
What Ruwth had to say.

01:22:28.224 --> 01:22:31.326
What Dowd acknowledges of the Amah that

01:22:31.645 --> 01:22:33.947
Yahowah offered him to release him from

01:22:35.007 --> 01:22:36.708
this horrible plight that he had placed

01:22:36.748 --> 01:22:37.269
himself in.

01:22:39.395 --> 01:22:41.537
I am going to walk you through those

01:22:41.577 --> 01:22:44.337
that we intermixed into this long

01:22:44.377 --> 01:22:48.121
presentation and then through the last

01:22:48.161 --> 01:22:49.582
word picture in its entirety.

01:22:49.601 --> 01:22:51.722
And I'll do so at the beginning of

01:22:51.762 --> 01:22:52.563
our next program.

01:22:52.582 --> 01:22:52.884
And as we do so,

01:22:52.904 --> 01:22:53.743
I'm going to move on to the follow-up

01:22:53.764 --> 01:22:54.664
prophecy to this, which is Yashayah Isaiah,

01:23:10.850 --> 01:23:11.530
Now from there,

01:23:12.091 --> 01:23:13.731
which will be many programs from now,

01:23:14.932 --> 01:23:16.033
I'm going to take you to where I

01:23:16.092 --> 01:23:20.055
am now in translating what Dowd did to

01:23:20.095 --> 01:23:21.354
require this intervention.

01:23:22.655 --> 01:23:25.716
So we have a lot to learn.

01:23:26.716 --> 01:23:29.537
That's a glorious place that God has

01:23:29.578 --> 01:23:29.979
brought us,

01:23:30.738 --> 01:23:33.539
completing his word picture and time for

01:23:33.600 --> 01:23:35.140
us to understand it and share it.

01:23:36.081 --> 01:23:37.841
So I thank all of you for

01:23:38.965 --> 01:23:42.092
listening for being part of this story and

01:23:42.113 --> 01:23:43.114
for sharing it with others.